---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/main.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="About Corey Burns" description="A quick look at Corey Burns and the work behind the blog.">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 md:px-10 py-28">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-[rgb(var(--color-text-muted))]">About</p>
      <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl md:text-6xl">Designing with intention, shipping with speed.</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-[rgb(var(--color-text-secondary))]">
        I’m Corey Burns, a full-stack product designer and engineer. I partner with teams to translate ambitious ideas into
        performant, human-centered experiences.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr]">
      <div class="glass-card rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 md:p-12 article-content">
        <p>
          My work blends design systems, frontend engineering, and rapid experimentation. I’m obsessed with crafting tools
          and interfaces that feel inevitable—simple, fast, and memorable.
        </p>
        <p>
          When I’m not building, I’m documenting processes, refining workflows, and exploring the future of creative AI.
        </p>
      </div>
      <aside class="glass-card rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 md:p-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl">Capabilities</h2>
        <ul class="mt-6 grid gap-4 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--color-text-secondary))]">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-[rgb(var(--color-border))] bg-[rgb(var(--color-bg-secondary)/0.7)] px-4 py-3">
            <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[rgb(var(--color-accent))]"></span>
            Product strategy + UX systems
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-[rgb(var(--color-border))] bg-[rgb(var(--color-bg-secondary)/0.7)] px-4 py-3">
            <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[rgb(var(--color-accent))]"></span>
            Frontend engineering + performance
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-[rgb(var(--color-border))] bg-[rgb(var(--color-bg-secondary)/0.7)] px-4 py-3">
            <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[rgb(var(--color-accent))]"></span>
            AI-powered design tooling
          </li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </section>
  </main>
</MainLayout>
